This article describes how to install the [[Haml]] bundle for [[TextMate]] via [[Subversion]].

= Installation =

<pre>cd Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles
# previously:
# svn co http://macromates.com/svn/Bundles/trunk/Bundles/Haml.tmbundle
# now:
svn co http://macromates.com/svn/Bundles/trunk/Bundles/Ruby%20Haml.tmbundle</pre>

= Post-installation =

If [[TextMate]] is running, go to the <tt>Bundles</tt> menu, open the <tt>Bundle Editor</tt> submenu and choose <tt>Reload Bundles</tt>.
